351
00:17:58,880 --> 00:18:00,330
<font size="21"><b>{\an7}BIRD D</b></font>

352
00:18:00,330 --> 00:18:03,790
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}INTELLEGENCE</b></font>

353
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Boom, baby! That put my Intelligence over 1,200.</font>

354
00:18:04,210 --> 00:18:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's try again: Share!</font>

355
00:18:06,130 --> 00:18:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It worked! I can share with up to six summons now!</font>

356
00:18:09,210 --> 00:18:11,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, my Intelligence stat was the key.</font>

357
00:18:12,500 --> 00:18:16,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now I know what the devs had in mind
when they gave Summoner such high intelligence.</font>

358
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wanna try using this skill
with my new summon creatures.</font>

359
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">First, create the remaining
five D-rank summon creatures!</font>

360
00:18:20,420 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}BIRD D</b></font>

361
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}INSECT D</b></font>

362
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}BEAST D</b></font>

363
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}STONE D</b></font>

364
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}GRASS D</b></font>

365
00:18:23,710 --> 00:18:25,710
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}FISH D</b></font>

366
00:18:24,920 --> 00:18:25,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now summon them!</font>

367
00:18:28,290 --> 00:18:30,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow! So, these are the D-ranks, huh?</font>

368
00:18:31,380 --> 00:18:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With the exception of Tatertot,
they all start with over 100 intelligence,</font>

369
00:18:34,170 --> 00:18:35,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">so they should understand me!</font>

370
00:18:36,130 --> 00:18:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hmm. Since I can use Share
and order them around...</font>

371
00:18:40,170 --> 00:18:44,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">isn't it feasible for me to hunt monsters
using nothing but my summons now?!</font>

372
00:18:44,750 --> 00:18:46,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let's try it and see!</font>

373
00:18:47,460 --> 00:18:48,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Target sighted!</font>

374
00:18:48,670 --> 00:18:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Spidey! Use Spider Silk!</font>

375
00:18:54,580 --> 00:18:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Teddy! Use Crush!</font>

376
00:18:59,670 --> 00:19:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bron! Use Protect!</font>

377
00:19:02,750 --> 00:19:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fillet! Use Spray!</font>

378
00:19:11,880 --> 00:19:15,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That gave a buff!
And it works on all my creatures!</font>

379
00:19:15,540 --> 00:19:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go kick ass, team!</font>

380
00:19:19,000 --> 00:19:21,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Awesome. They totally cleaned house.</font>

381
00:19:21,790 --> 00:19:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're not one-shotting anything yet,</font>

382
00:19:24,000 --> 00:19:28,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but Teddy's attack and Spidey's debuff
make pretty short work of C-rank monsters.</font>

383
00:19:29,830 --> 00:19:34,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tatertot's ability probably
recovers MP based on its name.</font>

384
00:19:34,790 --> 00:19:38,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Let me use up my remaining MP
on farming skill EXP.</font>

385
00:19:38,710 --> 00:19:42,080
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}MP:</b></font>

386
00:19:39,580 --> 00:19:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Tatertot, use your ability! Crop of Magic!</font>

387
00:19:52,920 --> 00:19:59,380
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}MP:</b></font>

388
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I got back 1,000 MP! Hell yeah!</font>

389
00:19:55,830 --> 00:19:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Finally an MP recovery item!</font>

390
00:20:01,040 --> 00:20:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I still haven't tested
Hollow's ability, Night Vision.</font>

391
00:20:03,960 --> 00:20:05,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But it's obviously the opposite of Hawkins.</font>

392
00:20:06,040 --> 00:20:08,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It should help me scout enemies at night.</font>

393
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which means...</font>

394
00:20:12,000 --> 00:20:15,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">my telecommand creature squadron
is ready for action!</font>

395
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:18,630
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}DAY</b></font>

396
00:20:15,790 --> 00:20:18,630
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}NIGHT</b></font>

397
00:20:15,880 --> 00:20:18,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hawkins and Hollow will scout for monsters.</font>

398
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:21,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fillet will buff everyone's evasion rate.</font>

399
00:20:22,130 --> 00:20:24,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then Spidey will cripple the enemy
while Teddy attacks them.</font>

400
00:20:25,420 --> 00:20:29,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can farm EXP every day of the month
using nothing but my summon creatures!</font>

401
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:32,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Talk about perfect!</font>

402
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:35,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fillet's buffs will boost
my Intelligence stat to 1,600.</font>

403
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:38,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I can use Share with eight summons, easy peasy!</font>

404
00:20:39,500 --> 00:20:43,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, team! Let's go monster hunting!</font>

405
00:20:43,380 --> 00:20:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Be careful to avoid all human adventurers.</font>

406
00:20:46,420 --> 00:20:48,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't attack them, even if they attack you.</font>

407
00:20:48,710 --> 00:20:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are we clear?</font>

408
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This new skill gives me so much more to do.</font>

409
00:20:57,170 --> 00:20:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Although it makes me feel kinda monstrous.</font>

410
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The White Dragon is just beyond
that mountain range, huh?</font>

411
00:21:07,710 --> 00:21:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I just had a great idea.</font>

412
00:21:10,330 --> 00:21:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There's one more way I can use the Share skill!</font>

413
00:21:13,750 --> 00:21:15,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My name is Krena the Fierce!</font>

414
00:21:15,630 --> 00:21:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dogora the Axe User! I challenge you!</font>

415
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A'ight! Bring it!</font>

416
00:21:27,380 --> 00:21:29,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Next! You're up, Mash!</font>

417
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay!</font>

418
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:41,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Never see birds like that around here.</font>

419
00:21:43,170 --> 00:21:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, Myulla. Settle down.</font>

420
00:21:47,710 --> 00:21:49,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There. All done.</font>

421
00:21:49,670 --> 00:21:51,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, mommy!</font>

422
00:21:56,670 --> 00:21:58,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A gold coin...?</font>

423
00:22:00,080 --> 00:22:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Happy to see the fam's doing well.</font>

424
00:22:05,130 --> 00:22:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll send you guys more every month.</font>

